body: "## Changes Required\\n\\n### 1) .github/workflows/release.yml\\n- Trigger on version tags (v*.*.*)\\n- Run full build + typecheck + test + coverage gate\\n- Then publish to npm via NODE_AUTH_TOKEN\\n- Upload coverage artifact\\n\\n### 2) ci.yml and nightly.yml\\n- Add Node 24 to CI matrix (ubuntu-latest + Node 24)\\n- Nightly: add Node 24 alongside 20 and 22\\n\\n### 3) PRD/README/AGENTS doc updates\\n- Update PRD Milestone 6 checklist to include release workflow\\n- Update README Release Readiness Checklist to mention release workflow\\n- Update CHANGELOG under [Unreleased]"
